files.name: README.md
files.content:
Chalk.ist

Create beautiful images of your source code

Go to App

[![](./.github/screenshot.png)](https://chalk.ist) ## Development ``` pnpm install ``` ``` pnpm run dev ``` ## License MIT - Kasper Mikiewicz 2022

files.name: drizzle.config.ts
nuxt.config.ts
package.json
files.content:
{
  "name": "chalk.ist",
  "private": true,
  "version": "0.1.0",
  "type": "module",
  "scripts": {
    "db:generate": "drizzle-kit generate",
    "db:migrate": "drizzle-kit migrate",
    "dev": "nuxt dev",
    "prepare": "nuxi prepare",
    "build": "vue-tsc --noEmit && nuxt build",
    "serve": "nuxt preview"
  },
  "prettier": {
    "tabWidth": 2,
    "printWidth": 80,
    "importOrderSeparation": false,
    "importOrderSortSpecifiers": true,
    "plugins": [
      "prettier-plugin-tailwindcss"

    "@iconify/vue": "4.1.1",
    "@nuxt/scripts": "^0.9.5",
    "@nuxthub/core": "^0.8.7",
    "@nuxtjs/tailwindcss": "^6.12.2",
    "@pinia/nuxt": "^0.5.5",
    "@shikijs/markdown-it": "1.24.0",
    "@shikijs/transformers": "1.24.0",
    "@tailwindcss/typography": "0.5.15",
    "@unhead/vue": "^1.11.13",
    "@vite-pwa/nuxt": "^0.10.5",
    "@vueuse/components": "11.1.0",
    "@vueuse/core": "11.1.0",
    "@vueuse/head": "^2.0.0",
    "@vueuse/integrations": "11.1.0",
    "drizzle-orm": "^0.36.4",
    "fflate": "0.8.2",
    "fuse.js": "6.5.3",
    "markdown-it": "13.0.2",
    "modern-screenshot": "4.4.39",
    "mp4-muxer": "^2.3.0",
    "nanoid": "5.0.9",
    "nuxt": "^3.13.2",
    "ofetch": "1.4.1",
    "pathe": "1.1.2",
    "pica": "7.1.0",
